// MyTable.js
import React from 'react'
import { Container, Row, Col } from 'reactstrap'

const MyTable = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
      <Row>
        <Col>.col</Col>
      </Row>
      <Row>
        <Col>.col</Col>
        <Col>.col</Col>
        <Col>.col</Col>
        <Col>.col</Col>
      </Row>
      <Row>
        <Col xs="3">.col-3</Col>
        <Col xs="auto">.col-auto - variable width content</Col>
        <Col xs="3">.col-3</Col>
      </Row>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default MyTable
